title: Ring Master
subTitle: Prince, a dog trainer, faces an awkward situation when his pet dog Diana acts in a film alongside his former lover, an actress who shares the same name as the dog.

title: Padheyam
subTitle: Chandradas, a renowned poet, accidentally meets his estranged teenaged daughter, Harita. After coaxing her, he takes her to his ancestral home, but she starts missing her stepfather.

title: Cheriya Kallanum Valiya Poleesum
subTitle: Sadasivan comes across a house where the owner, Kumaran, has committed suicide to protect his wife, Soumini. However, what is even stranger is that a man who is visually challenged is always around.

title: Bada Dosth
subTitle: Daya Shankar, a courageous police officer, befriends Geevarghese, a notorious criminal, and earns his trust. However, things get complicated after the policeman reveals the real reason for his friendship.

title: Chirikkum Thalika
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the best rib-tickling comedy scenes from various Malayalam movies featuring renowned actors and actresses.

title: Salala Mobiles
subTitle: A young mobile phone shop owner's life takes a turn after he gets his hands on a tapping app. Meanwhile, his heart finds comfort in the presence of a beautiful woman waiting at a bus stand nearby.

title: Mannar Mathai Speaking 2
subTitle: Mannar Mathai runs a travel agency with his friends, Gopalakrishnan and Balakrishnan. He wants to revive his drama group on its 25th anniversary but his friends refuse to act again.

title: Sound Thoma
subTitle: Thoma belongs to the Palaparambil family, which is disliked by the locals due to his father's actions. However, he comes up with a plan to portray his greedy father as a charitable person.

title: Oru Marubhoomikkadha
subTitle: Madhavan is an honest and hardworking man. However, when a rich man's daughter, Eliana, asks him to abduct her and demand a ransom from her father, his life turns upside down.

title: Su From So
subTitle: In the coastal village of Marlur, Ashoka's innocent crush sparks rumours of ghostly possession, creating comedic chaos and unexpected twists.

title: In Ghost House Inn
subTitle: Thomas Kutty buys a haunted bungalow and convinces his friends to stay with him on the first night. The trouble begins when they actually see the ghost of the mistress who was killed 70 years ago.

title: In Ghost House Inn
subTitle: Thomas Kutty buys a haunted bungalow and convinces his friends to stay with him on the first night. The trouble begins when they actually see the ghost of the mistress who was killed 70 years ago.

title: Killadi Raman
subTitle: Mahadevan is a live witness of Radhika's hit-and-run accident. His helpful gesture of taking Radhika to the hospital, however, lands him in trouble when he is confronted by Meera, Radhika's friend.

title: Janamaithri
subTitle: The officers at Paramedu police station start an innovative campaign to reach out to the residents of the area. However, things do not go as planned and they land in all sorts of trouble.

title: Kanakasimhasanam
subTitle: Kanakambaran runs a drama troupe that is deep in financial debt. In order to keep his dream afloat, he takes a job in which he has to act as the heir to the throne of a royal family.

title: Teja Bhai and Family
subTitle: Teja Bhai, a gangster falls in love with Vedhika, a simple girl. He has to leave his criminal life behind in order to seek her father's consent to marry her.

title: Dhrona
subTitle: A man sets out to investigate the death of his brother at a haunted house, leading him to come across several supernatural experiences.

title: Aavesham
subTitle: Three boys move into a hostel to pursue engineering, where they clash with seniors. To get revenge, they befriend a gangster.

title: Vaazha
subTitle: Four misfits navigate societal and parental pressures as they enter adulthood. Subsequently, their heartfelt journey of self-discovery proves that love and acceptance always triumph over judgment.

title: Rasathanthram
subTitle: Premachandran, a carpenter, rescues Kanmani, an ill-treated maid, and takes her into his care. However, to escape from her former abusers, Kanmani dresses up as a boy and joins the team of carpenters.

title: Ennum Eppozhum
subTitle: Vineeth, a magazine reporter, lacks the inspiration to work hard. However, his life takes a turn when he is asked to interview a family court lawyer.

title: Ennum Eppozhum
subTitle: Vineeth, a magazine reporter, lacks the inspiration to work hard. However, his life takes a turn when he is asked to interview a family court lawyer.

title: Monayi Angane Aanayi
subTitle: Monayi goes to the city to stay with his friend. However, he ends up getting involved in problems which turns chaotic for everyone.

title: Jananam 1947 Pranayam Thudarunnu
subTitle: In a care home for the elderly, two senior citizens forge a heartwarming connection, embarking on a shared path of love and companionship.

title: Hailesa
subTitle: Unnikrishnan is forced to move to the city after he beats up some thugs for his foster family. In the city, he starts working for Ganapathy Iyer, a rich man who is seeking his long-lost lover.

title: June
subTitle: June, a teenager, believes that there is nothing remarkable about her. She experiences adolescent crushes, handles heartbreaks and fights insecurities as she grows into a mature and confident woman.

title: One
subTitle: An aspiring policeman embarks on an unauthorised mission to investigate a devious scientist. However, he confronts various challenges when his actions are exposed.

title: Snehaveedu
subTitle: Ajayan comes back to his village to be with his ailing mother. However, things get strange when a boy comes to his house claiming to be his son.

title: Oru Vadakkan Selfie
subTitle: When his father asks him to manage their grocery store, Umesh runs away to Chennai to become a film-maker. His life changes after he takes a selfie with his old neighbour and posts it online.

title: Lucifer
subTitle: The demise of the leader of a political party leads to a massive power struggle. Amidst the chaos, a mystical man named Stephen comes in to ascend the throne.

title: Love Action Drama
subTitle: Dinesh, a conceited and wealthy young bachelor, goes to extreme lengths to impress a girl named Shobha with the help of his best friend Sagar, and Dinesh eventually hopes to marry Shobha.
